comments.comment:
Astolfo is a character from the legend of Charlemagne, France's most famous tale of chivalry.
One of the Twelve Paladins of Charlemagne, and a prince of England.
Additionally, a screwed-up Heroic Spirit who has lost all rationality.

Height/Weight: 164cm, 56kg
Origin: Legend of Charlemagne
Region: France
Alignment: Chaotic-Good
Gender: ???
As per Astolfo's request, their gender is a secret.

The Twelve Paladins were knights who served Charlemagne, the King of Franks.
Astolfo, cousin of Roland, was one of those twelve knights.
However, according to legends, Astolfo was considered one of the weakest amongst the knights.

Out of control, inexperienced, careless, etc, etc.
But despite such a reputation, the Knight Astolfo overcame a number of difficult tasks.
By the way, Astolfo's dressed this way to calm Roland down after being rejected.

Astolfo has lost all rationality, so instead of making judgements based off of merits, Astolfo makes all choices based off "if it feels good or not."
That hasn't changed since being summoned as a Servant, but since Astolfo is a good person, there isn't too much to worry about.

Also, while Astolfo may be weak, their numerous Noble Phantasms received through their countless adventures are very powerful and reliable.
But, it is very difficult to control Astolfo.

Since Astolfo doesn't have a specific wish for the Grail, everything depends on if their Master is likeable or not.
Regardless of gender, Astolfo will follow loved ones to the bitter end.

voiceLines.name: Birthday
voiceLines.subtitle: Happy birthday! I hope you have a wonderful day!

voiceLines.name: During an Event
voiceLines.subtitle: Hey, hey, Master! Something's up, let's go check it out!

voiceLines.name: Conversation 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Hm? Well, I am your Servant, after all. I'll do my best!

voiceLines.name: Conversation 3
voiceLines.subtitle: Yes, yes. That's why you gotta show me how cool you are too!

voiceLines.name: Likes
voiceLines.subtitle: Things that I like? Everything! I like everything in this world except for the things I hate!

voiceLines.name: Dislikes
voiceLines.subtitle: Things that I hate? Hmm, nothing. I like almost everything in this world!

voiceLines.name: About the Holy Grail
voiceLines.subtitle: The Holy Grail? I don't really care about it. But if you want to acquire it, then I'll give my full support! Hehe

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Don't just touch a maiden's fair skin! Huh? Did I say something strange?

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 3
voiceLines.subtitle: Quit touching me, you've been at it non-stop since you summoned me! Don't make me use force! Haha, take this!

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 4
voiceLines.subtitle: Hm? Is it tough not having any common sense? Well, I guess so. But you know, there are things that only I can understand because I lack common sense.

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 5
voiceLines.subtitle: I am your sword, blade, and arrow, Master! You have placed your trust in me, despite how weak I am. I won't let you down!

voiceLines.name: Level up
voiceLines.subtitle: Yay! I've gotten a bit stronger!

voiceLines.name: Ascension 1
voiceLines.subtitle: [id 400400_0_G030]Woo! I can't get enough of this!

voiceLines.name: Summon
text: Yahoo! My name is Astolfo! Rider Class!
voiceLines.subtitle:
Yahoo! My name is Astolfo! Rider Class!
And, and...umm, nice to meet you!

voiceLines.name: Battle Start 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Astolfo of the Twelve Paladins of Charlemagne! Be like a falling leaf! But don't actually fall!

voiceLines.name: Battle Start 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Give me a minute to get ready! Okay, come at me!

voiceLines.name: Victory 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Not even a challenge! Oh, the title of the weakest belongs to you now. Is that okay?

voiceLines.name: Victory 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Perfect! I'm tired so I'm gonna take a little rest, see you later!

voiceLines.name: Incapacitated 2
voiceLines.subtitle: I'm sorry, I can't go on...

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 1
voiceLines.subtitle:
Heh heh. Did you see the lineup!?
I worked reeeal hard collecting them, so hurry up and exchange already!

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 2
voiceLines.subtitle:
Good work.
Do you want to eat first? Take a bath first? Or maybe you want to exchange. With. Me. First? Teehee.

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 3
voiceLines.subtitle:
By the way, you don't maybe know what I was thinking just a second ago, do you...?
What I was trying to look up on my phone...? Hmmm...

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 4
voiceLines.subtitle:
Hmmm, do you want to exchange that? Or this? It's such a tough choice...
Well...you just need to exchange them all! Good luck!

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 5
voiceLines.subtitle:
Want to do an exchange?
Here you go! That's my TMitter handle!
Eh? You're not asking for that? Do you want Mordred's instead?

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 6
voiceLines.subtitle:
All done!
My part-time job's over! Master, take me out to dinner instead of paying me!
Oh, but if you have some exchanging left to do, I'll still do it!

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 7
voiceLines.subtitle:
You did good during the event!
It's a little sad to think that this'll be the last time I get to talk to you like this.
Okay then, let's finish up whatever you have left!

voiceLines.name: About Spiritron Dress
voiceLines.overwriteName: About Spiritron Dress Memories at Trifas
voiceLines.subtitle:
Okay! Let's leave Chaldea, head down the mountain, and go to the city!
No? We really can't?
Even for a date with someone as cute as ME!?

voiceLines.name: Level up
voiceLines.subtitle: Yay! I've gotten a bit stronger!

voiceLines.name: Unlock Wardrobe
voiceLines.subtitle:
[id 400400_11_G060]Hm, this? They're civilian clothes I bought a while ago! [id 400400_11_G061]What do you think? Looks good on me, right!?
[id 400400_11_G062]See, the hoodie has bunny ears!
[id 400400_11_G063]The bunny ears are cute, right!? Hop! Hop!

voiceLines.name: Battle Start 1
voiceLines.subtitle:
What? I don't wanna bring my work home with me...
Just kidding!

voiceLines.name: Battle Start 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Being very careful not to get my outfit dirty...

voiceLines.name: Victory 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Yay! Biiig victory! And now Astolfo takes his leave...

voiceLines.name: Noble Phantasm Card
voiceLines.overwriteName: Noble Phantasm Card Memories at Trifas
voiceLines.subtitle: Leave it to me!
